            <description><![CDATA[[我走了]<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8D%E4%B9%85%E5%9D%90%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A5%E6%95%91%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E4%B8%8D%E4%B9%85%E5%9D%90%E7%9A%84%E8%A1%A5%E6%95%91%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不得不久坐的补救方法#</span></a> 搬砖人久坐必备的拉伸动作，不仅能增强脊柱肌肉力量，还能改善关节灵活度，坐着就能练！摸鱼动起来<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%E7%B4%A0%E5%85%BB%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87v%E8%AE%A1%E5%88%92%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#健康素养提升v计划#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4879939531636914" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hc1qfwdn0jj61w112atz702.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/vFzTBJYzlx083UJUBPDq01041200khq60E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1700169219&amp;ssig=BiL6U0arpR&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/E0Ul3PMQlx083UJTDwxO010412009QGT0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=